---
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
import LandingPage from "../layouts/LandingPage.astro";
---

<LandingPage title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>
      Chrome Key<br />
      <span class="highlight">Bioinformatics</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="tagline">
      Separates what matters from what doesn't<br />
      in your data and in your research questions.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-container">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Let's Work Together</a>
      <a href="#about" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="story" id="about">
    <div class="story-container">
      <h2 class="section-title">The Chrome Key Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="story-content">
        <p>
          During my PhD at Penn, I developed a method called <span
            class="greenscreen-highlight">Greenscreen</span
          > for filtering artifacts from ChIP-seq data. The concept was simple: use
          the tools already in your toolkit to remove the background noise obscuring
          your signal.
        </p>
        <p>
          That's still how I approach every project. Whether it's genomic
          analysis, statistical genetics, or pipeline development, I help you
          see through the noise to the biology beneath.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Add more sections as needed -->
</LandingPage>

<style>
  .hero {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 4rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .hero .highlight {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hero .tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .cta-container {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .btn {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--background);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(224, 122, 95, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(224, 122, 95, 0.4);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--accent-teal);
    border: 3px solid var(--accent-teal);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-teal);
    color: var(--background);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .story {
    background: var(--background-cream);
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  .story-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--accent-teal);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .story-content {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--gray);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .story-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .greenscreen-highlight {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero .tagline {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .cta-container {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
